{"tid":2516622,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"本 HR 向老細提議 Lunch Time 節食提神計劃，減少員工午後工作效率下降問題","createTime":"2021-05-04T18:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:26:45.000Z","uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abc62f4b51efe85e30593a6276310ef0595ee3a1","tid":2516622,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"返咗幾年工由小薯 HR 做到 HR manager 都發現有唔少同事食飽飯後話飯氣攻心, 眼訓, 於是lunch time 後嘅工作效率, 態度, 開會氣氛都大不如前<br />\n<br />\n原因就係因為你地 lunch time 食太飽食太急同埋食太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以下個禮拜開始參考外國嘅lunch set , 中午只可以進食三文治 / 水果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> OT 前晚餐可以買一個飯兩位同事分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望各位提高工作效率"},{"pid":"db4d65c8e15623714fc1bf7e26324572a0e56561","tid":2516622,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"Ching係赤柱做？"}]}